name: whathub_last_message_out_agent
label: Email of the agent that of the agent involved in the last WhatsApp message sent from the HubSpot UI
description: Email of the agent that sent the last message from the HubSpot UI. It does not include messages sent from the phone or WhatsApp Web

name: whathub_last_message_out_date
label: Date of the last WhatsApp message sent from the HubSpot UI
description: Date of the last message sent to a contact from the HubSpot UI. It does not include messages sent from the phone or WhatsApp Web

label: Date of the last WhatsApp conversation synced
description: Date of the last time the sync process run and found new messages for this contact. This includes both incoming and outgoing messages

name: whathub_last_message_synced_full
label: Full JSON payload of the last WhatsApp conversation synced
description: All data of the event recorded the last time the sync process run and found new messages for this contact. This includes both incoming and outgoing messages
